        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-954",
        "content": "Kingston.--Instructive remarks on early English history.--Instructive observations on carved oak and life in general.--Sad case of Stivvings, junior.--Musings on antiquity.--I forget that I am steering.--Interesting result.--Hampton Court Maze.--Harris as a guide.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
