        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-954",
        "content": "Years later, to the crash of battle music, Saxon kings and Saxon revelry were buried side by side, and Kingston's greatness passed away for a time, to rise once more when Hampton Court became the palace of the Tudors and the Stuarts, and the royal barges strained at their moorings on the river's bank, and bright cloaked gallants swaggered down the water steps to cry: \"What Ferry, ho!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-954_130627_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/954/130627/954_130627_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-954",
        "content": "Gadzooks, gramercy.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-954_130627_000012_000000",
