        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-954",
        "content": "Thoughtless friends jeer at it, and even my landlady herself has no admiration for it, and excuses its presence by the circumstance that her aunt gave it to her.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
